Java script is a dynamically typed pogramming language used to create modern websites and applications that contains dynamic content.
In javascript the data type of variable is decided at run time that's why its called dynamically types language. 
it is used for both front-end and backend developement.
java script is a single threaded language and performs one task at a time.
its an interpreted language it means it executes mutilpe line fo code one by one.


HTML defines content of webpage.
CSS adds style to it.
Javascript adds behaviour and logic to it.
It can update and change both HTML and CSS.

hello world program in java script..........



<html>
<head></head>
<body>
    <h1>Check the console for the message!</h1>
    <!-- Script tag is used to write javascript code in html file -->
    <script>
        // This is our first JavaScript program
       console.log("hello world!");
    </script>
</body>
</html>



